                     <interp inst="t17890603-74-off360" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17890603-74-cd361" type="crimeDate">9th of May</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17890603-74-off360 t17890603-74-cd361"></join> last, one piece of woollen cloth, containing thirty-eight yards, value 8 l. the property of 
                     
